metadata.name: Related to the world
metadata.description:
Photo: 3904  x  6960px.

This is 1 unique NFT from the "Open Your Eyes, It's Art" collection.

Man is nature, a part of it, an extension of it. Man is the whole world, and at the same time a grain of sand in the universe. A black and white flower on the earth. We can be alone until we open our eyes.
